data.description: Offering two master bedrooms! VA Assumable with 2.6% Interest Rate. This stunning home features a whopping 3,159 sq. ft. with wood-like tile throughout the main living area, high ceilings with crown molding, recessed lighting, upgraded fixtures, a gas fireplace, a covered back patio, and a fenced-in backyard with a cozy fire pit. Beyond the spacious foyer, the home flows into an open concept living, dining, and kitchen area. The kitchen is equipped with 42'' upgraded staggered white cabinets, a tile backsplash, stainless-steel appliances (including a gas cooktop), granite countertops, and an oversized island with ample seating. You'll appreciate the incredible storage options, including three pantries, keeping your kitchen organized and clutter-free. In a private wing, the master suite features Trey ceilings. The en-suite bathroom boasts a double vanity, a soaking tub, a large tiled walk-in shower, and a generous master closet complete with built-in shelving. Off the foyer, you'll find two guest bedrooms and a charming bathroom with shiplap, adding a touch of Florida style. Behind the kitchen, there's a separate wing where you'll find the second master bedroom with an en-suite bathroom and walk-in closet perfect for multigenerational living, accommodating guests, or simply additional luxury and comfort within the home. This area offers both privacy and convenience, with direct access to the 3-car garage and a spacious laundry room. The second level offers a versatile bonus room, providing ample space to transform this gorgeous home into a five-bedroom haven with plenty of space to spare! In addition, this home also benefits from underground utilities, ensuring unobstructed views and enhancing the overall aesthetic appeal of the highly desirable subdivision. With a blend of luxury, comfort, and functionality, it's the perfect place to call home!
